reviewText: We absolutely love this movie. Fast service great price.

I saw Doug at the Superdome in New Orleans
1978 when I was 10, ride the entire super cross track on a wheelie and then .. ride it backwards with a passenger .. been a fan ever since.
  This is a great documentary of his life

A good video on Doug Domokos. I only wish they had included footage of him doing wheelies on more of a variety of motorcycles such as say a Kawasaki KZ1300 which I've seen photos of him doing a wheelie on!
